snippet.title: ACLU responds! Amber's friends get Subpoenaed!
snippet.description:
Hello everyone! The ACLU has responded to Johnny Depp's SIX subpoenas!

Johnny Depp and his team also subpoena Amber Heard's friends. We have the subpoena who was sent to Tillett Wright, who is a friend of Amber. This guy has went above and beyond Amber's other fiends. He testified in the UK trial and he also wrote an article in June 2016 called "Why I Called 911."

The full article: "Why I Called 911" - https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/2016/06/113149/domestic-violence-911-call-famous-friend

Other Videos on these subjects - 

ACLU responds to Johnny Depp subpoenas regarding Amber Heard donations -  https://youtu.be/OlKeX-0vGD4

Heard panics! As her friends get served?! New Proof says they'll crack! - https://youtu.be/IDDCmNnpQ3s

My other videos on Johnny Depp and Amber Heard

Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard: The Complete Story - https://youtu.be/CMxp-tlyQrw

Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard: The Complete Story part 2 - https://youtu.be/JsMEJhMjTGA

BOMBSHELL NEWS! ACLU planned all of this with Amber! - https://youtu.be/--Te2eW6viU

Huge Win For Johnny Depp in Court! Amber faces multiple felony charges! - https://youtu.be/gDWbSNcW0aI

My Equipment I Use - 
The video footage was shot using a Canon EOS M50 Mark 2
My microphone is a Blue Yeticaster professional broadcast bundle. With yeti USB microphone, Radius 3 shockmount, and Compass Boom Arm
The lighting I use is a GVM bicolor LED video light
The video editing program I use is Cyberlink Powerdirector 365 version 19
